        , 11: [ {class: "vs", text: "Who then should make more mourning, she, that has lost so great a multitude, or you, which are grieved but for one?"} ]
        , 12: [ {class: "vs", text: "but if you say to me, My lamentation is not like the earth’s, for I have lost the fruit of my womb, which I brought forth with pains, and bare with sorrows:"} ]
